The copyist of G, having had to write quotz'ens ego twice over in 5 18, inserts ego after quotiens when it occurs for the third time. (1) Impers. indic. act. of 1st conjugation confused with present: 5 4 celebrantur for celebrabantur in Ε. Stuerenburg and others vainly defend the present as a historical present.
